      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that simple though. \"tiny steps\" don't work when the cycle is this heavy. it's like i've tried every small step there is and the loop just resets anyway. i'm just tired of fighting it. it feels like the only way to actually stop the cycle is to just... stop everything. the loop only ends one way.",
